{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1678-06e_226", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Lettre XXVIII"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Extraordinaire du Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", quartier d’avril 1678 (tome II), p. 226-228."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Lettre XXVIII."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "À Auxerre"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "VOs Ouvrages, Monsieur, font tant de bruit dans le monde, qu’il faudroit n’en estre pas pour ne les point lire. Toutes les Lettres qui composent vostre Extraordinaire, nous ont donné beaucoup de plaisir ; & apres avoir bien resvé sur l’Histoire Enigmatique, nous avons crû l’entendre dans son vray sens, en l’expliquant sur "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "le Canal de Languedoc"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[2]", "text": ", qui doit faire "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "la jonction des deux Mers"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[3]", "text": ". Nous n’avons pas eu moins de satisfaction à lire vostre Mercure du Mois de May ; & ce qui nous l’en renduë plus sensible, a esté "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[3]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[3]/text()[1]", "text": "la Fluste"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[4]", "text": ", que nous avons trouvée dans vostre premiere Enigme ; & comme la Fluste s’accomode fort bien avec le Tambour, nous n’avions point douté d’abord que ce mot de "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[4]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Tambour"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[5]", "text": " ne fust celuy de vostre Enigme ; mais apres un peu de refléxion, nous avons connu que nous nous estions trompées. Nous ne sçavons si "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[5]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[5]/text()[1]", "text": "le Croissant de la Lune"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[6]", "text": " vous satisfera davantage. Vous nous l’apprendrez, Monsieur, par vostre Mercure de Juin, qu’attendent avec impatience vos tres-humbles Servantes,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Merces"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "l’aisnée"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": ", "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/hi[3]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/hi[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Odinet"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/text()[2]", "text": "."}]}]}]}